txt.en: You have explored the Limlight Gorge in Great River.
You have spoken with the spirits of the Limlight Gorge.
You have found traces of the ancient legacy of the Limlight Gorge, when it was still a part of the Golden Wood ages ago.
You have lent aid to many folk in the Limlight Gorge.
Your efforts have earned you great respect among the Heroes of Limlight Gorge.

Complete Quests of the Limlight Gorge Deed
